title: URL Vulnerablility Check: Achilles
description: Achilles is a personal project that checks URLS for vulnerabilities with regards to form, comments, and passwords. It will scan through website HTML code to check for issues and finally reports the findings to a txt file of your choosing. STANDARD BUILD: achilles.py <YOUR HTTP/HTTPS WEBSITE HERE> -o report.txt

title: FREECycle Site Prototype
description: FREEcycle is a prototype website that will provide the staff, faculty and students of Seattle University a safe and easy way to reuse and upcycle items within the community that would otherwise be thrown away.  This project will not only benefit the university by being a low maintenance, self-policing system for reducing waste, but also benefit the staff and students by providing free access to items that they may need. Development included C#, Razor, .NET, javascript, and Sprint development.
